conditioning, protection, and technology upgrades for future Standard Missile-6 and Tomahawk missile variants. This effort
also includes design, integration, and testing activities to ensure the Reduced BOC Footprint (RBF) meets established system
objectives and maintains operational effectiveness. Provides systems engineering and government program management
required to manage development activities.
