fuel cell dock, design work to remove/replace an elevator in the Benefield Anechoic Facility, and control room upgrades for the
Joint Simulation Environment (JSE).
FY 2027 Plans:
412 TW FY 2027 Budget Year plans include multiple phased secure facility, power, and test cooling system upgrades for the
Benefield Anechoic Facility; multiple upgrades to the test engineering software lab to include HVAC replacement, safety/security
improvements, fire suppression system replacement and renovation of the warehouse storage and loading dock; and fire alarm
distribution upgrades for the telemetry van maintenance shop.
