to include design and build of REACH collaborative networks and IT infrastructure such as RAPID-MLS and
other supporting systems. Inform future architectures and NC3 modernization through technology evaluation,
assessment, demonstration, experimentation, prototyping, or development in a secure environment in support
of NC3 REACH CONOPS objectives. Develop and execute proof of concept applying modeling, simulation, and
analysis in support of NC3 modernization and technology transfer.

