Nebraska Defense Research Corporation (NDRC). One or more Collaborative Project Orders (CPO) will be
issued under the PIA to address the scope of PIA effort. Efforts will include completion of RAPID core services
as well as connection and interface with extended government networks as available. Approximately $6M to
multiple government agencies for circuits, engineering, and related communications services. No other FAR-
based contracts are anticipated under this effort.
