and convert them into well-defined technical problems. Those problems are then solved through pioneering research in AI, autonomy, and efficient computing or through
new applications of existing, state-of-the-art commercial technologies. The Studio partners with industry and academia to rapidly prototype, test, and field solutions that
deliver measurable strategic advantages. The Studio is the Air Force Pathfinder's vanguard project in deploying in connecting its network of bespoke talent to solve the
Air Force's technical problems. It's manning and talent development program, which helps to create PhD and Master's-level engineering expertise, is managed by and
through the Pathfinder program.

