systems; solve capability gaps; develop, acquire, upgrade, sustain, and/or support interoperable equipment with our allies; create cooperative acquisition, production, or
logistic partnerships; promote mutual and equitable sharing of effort, cost, information, and risk; provide access to remote or operational test sites; leverage economies
of scale; and promote interoperability with our allies.

