Description: Support JTMS Implementation Contract award through pre-acquisition and acquisition activities. This includes
drafting management plans, executing programmatic activities (Project Management, Configuration Management, Risk
Management, Release Management, Testing, and Training), providing solution analysis and recommendations to the Functional
Sponsor based on alternatives analysis, procuring and establishing the hosting environment, and initiating Risk Management
Framework (RMF) accreditation activities.

