E. Acquisition Strategy
Programmed funds continue to support Technology Maturation and Risk Reduction (TMRR) efforts. Organic resources are being utilized for the ongoing TMRR efforts.
The IS-ICD is complete with AFGSC/A5 coordinating associated Requirements Definition Packages (RDPs). Following the Acquisition Strategy Panel (ASP) on March
4, 2026, the program has adopted the Software Acquisition Pathway. The pending Acquisition Decision Memorandum (ADM) signature will authorize the program to
officially enter the planning phase. Continued organic development and contract award is expected in FY27.




